      "id": "PopularPost310252",
      "post_content": "Risky card. A p/t of 7/5 for five mana is pretty neat. In the worst case, your opponent uses the extra mana to cast some powerful spells and finishes his turn with killing this guy. Still, your opponent will be the first player, to make really good use of this ability, and it's also more vulnerable than, say, [mana reflection](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=mana reflection) or mirari's wake. ",
