    {
      "id": "PopularPost311665",
      "post_content": "Tricky card to play with; you most likely tap out to cast this card, so your opponent gets to be the first to play with double mana on his turn. And you don't want to go doubling your opponents mana right before they're ready to cast [Sphinx's Revelation](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name= Sphinx's Revelation)/[Rakdos's Return](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rakdos's Return)!   \n  \nHowever, if you start with [Yeva, Nature's Herald](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Yeva, Nature's Herald), then you can flash this in at the end of your opponent's turn! Then hopefully you can pour that mana into something devastating, maybe even something ridiculous like [Skarrg Goliath](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Skarrg Goliath) and [Boros Charm](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Boros Charm).",
      "posted_by": "TheChort",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost311665\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">Tricky card to play with; you most likely tap out to cast this card, so your opponent gets to be the first to play with double mana on his turn. And you don't want to go doubling your opponents mana right before they're ready to cast<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\" Sphinx's Revelation\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name= Sphinx's Revelation\"> Sphinx's Revelation</a>/<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Rakdos's Return\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rakdos's Return\">Rakdos's Return</a>! <br/><br/>However, if you start with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Yeva, Nature's Herald\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Yeva, Nature's Herald\">Yeva, Nature's Herald</a>, then you can flash this in at the end of your opponent's turn! Then hopefully you can pour that mana into something devastating, maybe even something ridiculous like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Skarrg Goliath\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Skarrg Goliath\">Skarrg Goliath</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Boros Charm\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Boros Charm\">Boros Charm</a>.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '311665'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted 